             sworn.</p>
               <p>On Friday morning last, I came to town with a load of fruit, and had it unloaded in Newgate-market; I staid there till near three; and when I heard a coffee-house was open, I went to get a dish of tea; during my absence, the prisoner took the sieve of apples, and the watchman took her afterwards with the property on her.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17880910-73-person635">
