                     <interp inst="t17880910-73-person635" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a watchman; I took the woman near the market with the sieve of apples on her.</p>
               <p>(Produced and deposed to.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I did it out of poverty.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17880910-73-verdict314" type="verdictDescription">
